attr.title: Flip of Dark
attr.desc:
A small precision platformer where you can instantly flip onto the ceiling and walls. You lost your slice of fruit, and have to get it back.
Flip of Dark is a fangame for Flip of Light, by Leko.
attr.inst: Download flipofdark.zip from itch.io and unzip the contents to ports/flipofdark/assets
attr.inst_md: Download flipofdark.zip from [itch.io](https://antidissmist.itch.io/flip-of-dark) and unzip the contents to ports/flipofdark/assets
